snippet.title: Convert a Fraction to a Decimal or Percent
snippet.description:
How to Convert Fractions Decimals and Percents in this free math video tutorial by Mario's Math Tutoring. We also look at a number of examples.

0:31 Example 1 Converting 5/8 to a Decimal & Percent
1:54 Example 2 Converting .22 to a Fraction & Percent
2:46 Example 3 Converting 140 Percent to a Decimal & Fraction
3:44 Example 4 Converting 2/5 to a Decimal & Percent
4:30 Example 5 Converting 3.2 to a Percent & Fraction
5:08 Example 6 Converting 2 Percent to a Decimal & Fraction
